    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026117_2_23759-23796",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "23759-23796",
      "markText": "任何一个人，只在努力程度上下功夫，不在可替代性方面下功夫，结果都会很难看。",
      "totalCount": 845,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026117&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=23759&rangeEnd=23796",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/93a32c50813ab70b3g017b11?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=23759&rangeEnd=23796"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026117_2_15171-15217",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "15171-15217",
      "markText": "你想说服一个人去改变思维方式，或者跟你一起做事，不要靠嘴，要用你自己变得强大了这件事去改变。",
      "totalCount": 816,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026117&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=15171&rangeEnd=15217",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/93a32c50813ab70b3g017b11?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=15171&rangeEnd=15217"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026117_2_5258-5309",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "5258-5309",
      "markText": "我很少给别人意见，为什么？因为每个人受自身经验和认知水平的限制，很多时候分不清什么是善意、什么是欺骗。",
      "totalCount": 726,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026117&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=5258&rangeEnd=5309",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/93a32c50813ab70b3g017b11?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=5258&rangeEnd=5309"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026117_2_2987-3064",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "2987-3064",
      "markText": "1. 做的事要有复利性、可积累性，随着时间推移，可以积少成多。 2. 不偏离你的主航道，一鱼多吃。",
      "totalCount": 720,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026117&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=2987&rangeEnd=3064",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/93a32c50813ab70b3g017b11?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=2987&rangeEnd=3064"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026117_2_6487-6529",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "6487-6529",
      "markText": "框架比努力更重要。什么是框架？就是你要知道面前这个事物的整体数据、规模、比例、趋势。",
      "totalCount": 646,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026117&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=6487&rangeEnd=6529",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/93a32c50813ab70b3g017b11?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=6487&rangeEnd=6529"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026117_2_648-681",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "648-681",
      "markText": "你这辈子给自己定的财富目标上限是多少？是一个亿，还是千万元的级别？",
      "totalCount": 644,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026117&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=648&rangeEnd=681",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/93a32c50813ab70b3g017b11?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=648&rangeEnd=681"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026117_2_6262-6288",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "6262-6288",
      "markText": "悲观者往往正确，乐观者往往成功，我不和悲观的人说话。",
      "totalCount": 555,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026117&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=6262&rangeEnd=6288",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/93a32c50813ab70b3g017b11?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=6262&rangeEnd=6288"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026117_2_2153-2180",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "2153-2180",
      "markText": "生意规模的上限，决定了你不可能赚到超出你生意规模的钱。",
      "totalCount": 544,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026117&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=2153&rangeEnd=2180",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/93a32c50813ab70b3g017b11?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=2153&rangeEnd=2180"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026117_8_31403-31452",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "31403-31452",
      "markText": "年轻人的黑夜当然漫长，漫长到你以为天亮永远都不会来了。但是，看过日出的人都知道，天亮是一瞬间的事。",
      "totalCount": 533,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026117&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=31403&rangeEnd=31452",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/93a32c50813ab70b3g017b11?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=31403&rangeEnd=31452"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026117_3_44319-44355",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "44319-44355",
      "markText": "我们不要抱着一颗玻璃心渴望别人的喜欢，要把精力放在自己身上，让自己变强。",
      "totalCount": 496,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026117&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=44319&rangeEnd=44355",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/93a32c50813ab70b3g017b11?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=44319&rangeEnd=44355"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026117_4_10355-10424",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "10355-10424",
      "markText": "我研究任何一个领域，都会看三类书籍：一类是这个领域有影响力的著作，一类是这个领域中号称“几分钟速成”的系列图书，还有一类是这个领域的教材。",
      "totalCount": 480,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300026117&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=10355&rangeEnd=10424",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/93a32c50813ab70b3g017b11?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=10355&rangeEnd=10424"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300026117_3_7642-7699",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "7642-7699",
